{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"72b7db76e5","title":"关于起草财经问题报告给南汉宸的信","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"33ef3b298a","index":0,"year":1942,"month":12,"day":20,"articleId":"72b7db76e5","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"书信","id":"2a70b5d939","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji2","name":"毛泽东文集第二卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji2.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji2":{"comments":[{"id":"117f7cb2dc","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{},"index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":14,"text":"南汉宸（一八九五——一九六七），山西洪洞人。当时任陕甘宁边区政府财政厅厅长。"},{"id":"4229ac2d94","publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{},"index":2,"part_index":6,"offset":19,"text":"指毛泽东在《经济问题与财政问题》第七部分《关于发展自给工业》中，采用了南汉宸此前写的报告中关于被服问题的内容。"}],"contents":[{"id":"56accbd581","type":"title","text":"关于起草财经问题报告给南汉宸的信","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"117f7cb2dc","type":"appellation","text":"汉宸同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"4229ac2d94","type":"paragraph","text":"请你写的东西不知着手否？我要的是关于粮草、税收、金融、贸易四部分，每样要说政策，说工作，是向广大的干部说话，使他们看了懂得政策的方向，懂得工作的作法。在说政策说工作时，要批评错误意见，批评工作缺点，使他们有所警惕。每样要有点历史，有点分析，又有一九四三年应如何作法。请你从今天至星期四四天之内下一番苦功赶一下，于星期五日交我就好了，或在星期二三先将粮草一件交我，余在星期四五交我。金融、贸易二件请找银行与贸易局的人研究一下，粮、税你是熟的。你前交报告很好，只是向少数人说的，不是向广大干部说的，故须重写。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f968c0c7d6","type":"paragraph","text":"敬礼！","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5b773d4823","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8d89486ca0","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月二十日夜","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0887d3e863","type":"subtitle","text":"你写的被服部分我已采入工业问题里去了。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"23bd89c0d2","type":"paragraph","text":"根据人民出版社一九八三年出版的","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5ea672791c","type":"paragraph","text":"《毛泽东书信选集》刊印。","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji2","articleId":"72b7db76e5","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":470,"end":469}}}},"__N_SSG":true}